OL,6,FA convicted fraudster cleared of
OL,7,Fmurdering his wealthy wife has been
OL,8,Fblocked from inheriting her #4.4
OL,9,Fmillion estate after a judge ruled he
OL,10,Fdrowned her.
OL,12,F"Serial liar" Donald McPherson, 51,
OL,13,Fwas ordered to be found not guilty of
OL,14,Fthe murder of his wife Paula Leeson,
OL,15,F47, on a judge's direction to the jury
OL,16,Fhalfway through his trial in 2021.
