OL,6,FHe carried wads of cash rolled up in
OL,7,Felastic bands to give the impression
OL,8,Fof a man of means, but was in reality
OL,9,Fa "man of straw", Manchester Crown
OL,10,FCourt was told.
OL,12,FMs Leeson drowned in the swimming pool
OL,13,Fat a remote holiday cottage, booked by
OL,14,FMcPherson for a summer break in
OL,15,FDenmark in 2017.
