OL,6,FBut the judge in his murder trial
OL,7,Fruled that despite circumstantial
OL,8,Fevidence, a jury could not be sure to
OL,9,Fthe criminal standard - beyond
OL,10,Freasonable doubt - that he had killed
OL,11,Fher.
OL,13,FMs Leeson's family brought legal
OL,14,Fproceedings against McPherson at
OL,15,FManchester Civil Courts of Justice, to
OL,16,Fblock him benefiting from her death
OL,17,Fand her #4.4 million estate.
OL,19,FFollowing hearings earlier in 2024, Mr
OL,20,FJustice Richard Smith ruled McPherson
OL,21,Fhad killed his wife.
