OL,6,FGiving his ruling he said: "Don
OL,7,Fdeliberately and unlawfully killed
OL,8,FPaula by compressing her neck in an
OL,9,Farm lock rendering her unconscious and
OL,10,Fcausing her body to enter the pool to
OL,11,Fensure her drowning and death.
OL,13,F"Don's motive for unlawfully killing
OL,14,FPaula Leeson is clear: money."
OL,16,FMr Justice Smith said the "critical
OL,17,Fquestion" was how Ms Leeson came to be
OL,18,Fin the water, which was only 4ft deep,
OL,19,Fand unable to save herself.
