OL,6,FAnd despite running out of money, he
OL,7,Fwas paying about #500 a month on
OL,8,Finsurance policies.
OL,10,FMcPherson was not present or
OL,11,Frepresented in court and is believed
OL,12,Fto be living somewhere in the South
OL,13,FPacific.
OL,15,FMs Leeson, who was 5ft 5in, drowned in
OL,16,Fthe pool that was less than 4ft deep,
OL,17,Fthough she could swim and was an
OL,18,Fotherwise healthy mother of one.
