OL,6,FBorn Alexander James Lang and
OL,7,Foriginally from New Zealand, Mr
OL,8,FMcPherson met Ms Leeson in 2013, using
OL,9,Fa "cover story" of being an orphan to
OL,10,Fhide his past after serving jail time
OL,11,Ffor an #11 million bank fraud in
OL,12,FGermany.
OL,14,FHe claimed to be a property developer
OL,15,Fand Ms Leeson oversaw the skip hire
OL,16,Fpart of her family's successful ground-
OL,17,Fworking business that her father
OL,18,FWilly, 80, had built up in Sale,
OL,19,FGreater Manchester, after emigrating
