OL,6,FMs Leeson and her brother Neville
OL,7,Fstood to inherit the business.
OL,9,FMr McPherson was described as a
OL,10,F"Walter Mitty" who had changed his
OL,11,Fname multiple times, had 32
OL,12,Fconvictions spanning 15 years in three
OL,13,Fcountries, and whose previous wife and
OL,14,Ftheir child died in a house fire.
OL,16,FMr McPherson told police he awoke to
OL,17,Ffind Ms Leeson face down in the
OL,18,Fshallow swimming pool at a holiday
OL,19,Fcottage in remote western Denmark he
OL,20,Fhad booked for the couple, on 6 June
OL,21,F2017.
