OL,6,FHer death was initially treated as a
OL,7,Ftragic accident by the Danish
OL,8,Fauthorities ` though she had suffered
OL,9,F13 separate external injuries.
OL,11,FWithin hours Mr McPherson was
OL,12,Ftransferring thousands of pounds from
OL,13,Fher accounts to cover his debts, the
OL,14,Fcourt heard.
OL,16,FHe had also "systematically" deleted
OL,17,Fdata from his wife's phone which may
OL,18,Fhave explained what happened and
OL,19,Frefused to give police access to his
OL,20,Fown phone.
