OL,6,FSoon after, Mr McPherson cleared their
OL,7,Fhome in Sale of his late wife's
OL,8,Fpossessions and joined a bereavement
OL,9,Fgroup, Widowed And Young ` that he
OL,10,Fcalled "Tinder for widows."
OL,12,FHe was later arrested in the UK as
OL,13,Fpolice looked into his financial
OL,14,Fbackground.
OL,16,FMr McPherson has always denied any
OL,17,Finvolvement in his wife's death and
OL,18,Fafter he was acquitted of murder, in a
OL,19,Fstatement through his solicitors, he
OL,20,Fdescribed it as a "tragic accident".
