OL,6,FHis lawyers had argued Ms Leeson's
OL,7,Finjuries could be a result of her
OL,8,Frescue from the pool and resuscitation
OL,9,Fattempts and pathologists could not
OL,10,Frule out that she could have fainted
OL,11,For accidentally fallen into the pool
OL,12,Fand drowned.
OL,14,FMr McPherson's murder trial was
OL,15,Fdramatically halted in March 2021 by
OL,16,Ftrial judge Mr Justice Goose, ruling
OL,17,Finsufficient evidence to jurors to
OL,18,Fsafely convict as the prosecution case
OL,19,Fwas based on circumstantial evidence.
OL,20,FCrucially, an accidental death could
OL,21,Fnot be ruled out.
